Run linters, formatters, and type checkers

Usage: normalize tools lint [OPTIONS] [TARGET] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  run   Run linters (default)
  list  List available linting tools
  help  Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Arguments:
  [TARGET]  Target path to check (defaults to current directory)

Options:
  -f, --fix                  Fix issues automatically where possible
  -r, --root <ROOT>          Root directory (defaults to current directory)
  -t, --tools <TOOLS>        Specific tools to run (comma-separated, e.g., "ruff,oxlint")
  -c, --category <CATEGORY>  Filter by category: lint, fmt, type
      --sarif                Output in SARIF format
  -w, --watch                Watch for file changes and re-run on save
      --json                 Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>            Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty               Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact              Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help                 Print help
